٢. Imad-ud-Din, "The Results of the Controversy in North India with Mohammedans," Church Missionary Intelligencer (hereafter CMI) ١٠ (١٨٧٥): ٢٧٦.
٣. Lyle L. Vander Werff, Christian Mission to Muslims (Pasadena, Calif.: William Carey Press, ١٩٧٧), p. ٤٣.
٤. See A. Powell, Muslims and Missionaries in Pre-Mutiny India (London: Curzon Press, ١٩٩٢), pp. ١٣٣ - ٣٦.
٥. Pfander to Basel Mission, September ١, ١٨٣١, cited in "The Late Rev. Dr. Charles Gottlieb Pfander, D.D.," CMI, n.s., ٢ (April ١٨٦٦): ٩٨.',NULL,'319',NULL,NULL,'0');
INSERT INTO [b132410] VALUES (303,'. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
