١٣. Muir, Mohammedan Controversy, p. ٦٧.
١٤. K. G. Pfander, trans. R. H. Weakley, Balance of Truth (London: CMS, ١٨٦٧), p. ١٢١; see also Powell, Muslims and Missionaries, p. ١٥١.
١٥. Pfander, Balance of Truth, p. ١٢٣.
