Works by Pfander
- ... ١٨٤٠ Remarks on the Nature of Mohammedanism. Calcutta: Baptist Mission Press.
- ... ١٨٤٧ Hall al-ishkal (Urdu: Solution of difficulties). Agra: Tract Society.
- ... ١٨٥٥ Ikhitam dini mubahasa ka (Urdu: Conclusion of the religious debate). Agra: Tract Society.
- ... ١٩١٠ The Balance of Truth. Translated and revised by W. St. Clair-Tisdall. London: RTS. Reprint, Villach: Light of Life, ١٩٨٦.
